<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>HaiHand Admin - Quản trị hệ thống</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-sans">
    
    <header class="bg-yellow-400 shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">⚡ HaiHand System</h1>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <span class="font-bold">Hi, <%= user.name %></span>
                    <a href="/" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-slate-700">Vào trang Quản trị ➜</a>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/login" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-slate-700">Đăng nhập Admin</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="bg-yellow-400 pb-16 pt-10 text-center text-slate-900">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-black mb-4">Hệ thống quản lý HaiHand</h2>
        <p class="text-xl font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-80">Nơi kiểm duyệt tin đăng, quản lý người dùng và vận hành sàn thương mại điện tử đồ cũ lớn nhất xóm.</p>
        
        <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-600"><%= posts.length %></p>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">Tin đã duyệt</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">24/7</p>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">Hoạt động</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12 -mt-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="bg-slate-900 text-yellow-400 px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">New</span>
            Tin vừa được duyệt công khai
        </h3>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <% if (posts.length === 0) { %>
                <p class="text-slate-500 col-span-4 text-center py-10 bg-white rounded-xl shadow">Chưa có tin đăng nào được duyệt.</p>
            <% } %>

            <% posts.forEach(post => { %>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 group cursor-pointer">
                <div class="h-48 bg-gray-200 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="<%= post.image ? '/uploads/' + post.image : 'https://via.placeholder.com/400x300?text=No+Image' %>" 
                         class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-500">
                    
                    <span class="absolute bottom-2 left-2 bg-slate-900 text-yellow-400 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">
                        <%= post.category %>
                    </span>
                    <span class="absolute bottom-2 right-2 bg-white/90 text-slate-900 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded flex items-center">
                        📍 <%= post.location || 'Toàn quốc' %>
                    </span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-4">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1 truncate"><%= post.title %></h4>
                    <p class="text-red-600 font-black text-lg">
                        <%= post.price.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %> đ
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-dashed">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-xs">👤</div>
                            <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-bold"><%= post.author ? post.author.name : 'Ẩn danh' %></span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400"><%= new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('vi-VN') %></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% }) %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>